      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LIL COCKATOO (8) shows ability but remains a maiden after six starts. Racing consistently finishing in the money the last two starts. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Sure to be about the mark. MASK OF ZORRO (7) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (23.09) at this track behind Candy Pops in a Maiden. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expecting another good run. POLLY GOLD (1) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (20.81) at Traralgon behind Take A Iris in a Bottom Up - Maiden. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expected to feature. HAVING A LOOK (6) has been in the placings at her last two runs, most recently when second (24.85) in a Rank Limit - Maiden over 425m at Bendigo.",
